        <div class="small-12 columns hr-bottom">
            <aside class="content-supplement">
                <div class="as-header">
                    <h3>Poppler Win32 Overview</h3>
                </div>

                <div class="project-container">
                    
                    <p id="summary">Poppler/PopplerQt5 pre-built binaries for Win32 GCC</p>
                    
                    <p id="description">Poppler Win32 are pre-built binaries of the Poppler library, it includes libpoppler.dll.a and libpoppler-qt5.dll.a.<br>
<br>
We made these pre-built binaries since building Poppler (Especially with Qt5 support) is hard and not fully supported on Microsoft Windows.<br>
<br>
Poppler Win32 was tested using Qt 5.2.1 and Mingw32.<br>
<br>
&#34;Poppler is a PDF rendering library based on the xpdf-3.0 code base.&#34;</p>
                </div>
            </aside>
        </div>
        


        


        
